Author: RosieNP
Text: Try to slow down and feed yourself some real good. I'm not in a place where I can really give advice, but you should prioritize your health so you can get that job (or another). I'm a psychiatric nurse practitioner about to graduate and I know the pressure, but you can't only carrot sticks and be on top of your game. Maybe try a less extreme restriction? I'm thinking of harm reduction here... Just go slow.
